  <brief_title>Icotinib in Advanced Metastatic Patients With NSCLC Previously Treated With Chemotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Efficacy of Icotinib in Advanced Metastatic Patients With NSCLC Previously Treated With Chemotherapy: a Single-arm, Phase 3 Study</official_title>
