  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was a single-arm, multi-center, prospective, phase 3 trial aimed to evaluate the
      efficacy and safety of icotinib in patients with locally advanced or metastatic NSCLC after
      failure of at least one platinum-based chemotherapy regimen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
